<p>Today is #GivingNewsDay and your opportunity to make a tax-free donation to support The Colorado Sun&#8217;s Report for America corps member.</p>

<p><strong>Report for America</strong>, a nonprofit organization, places talented emerging journalists in local newsrooms to document under-covered issues and communities. Photojournalist <strong>Olivia Sun</strong> is our Report for America corps member.</p>

<p>A tax-free donation at <a target="_blank"  href="https://coloradosun.com/rfa?utm_source=newsletter&utm_source=The+Colorado+Sun+Newsletters&utm_campaign=SUNRISER_*|DATE:Ymd|*&utm_medium=email">coloradosun.com/rfa</a> goes directly to supporting <strong>Olivia Sun</strong>&#8217;s salary and work. Your gift makes her work possible.</p>

